{"tid":2268863,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"咁癲？魔迷想謝拉特教曼聯！","createTime":"2020-11-03T06:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T11:22:10.000Z","uid":72497,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6cb39195f38dba77bae2c855d4f11934d8261c96","tid":2268863,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:15:40.000Z","msg":"曼聯於周日英超主場以0:1不敵阿仙奴，紅魔粉絲不滿領隊蘇斯克查，竟然希望利物浦傳奇謝拉特過檔救亡。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯球迷Brett於電台talkSPORT一個phone-in節目表示，希望愛隊易帥，由現時執教格拉斯哥流浪的謝拉特（Steven Gerrard）接手，更指這是一個不費吹灰之力便可以作出的決定，「我將會花大錢，找謝拉特來代替蘇斯克查。」 <br />\n<br />\n這個想法令主持人Darren Ambrose也大吃一驚，Brett解釋：「聽住，有錢使得鬼推磨。謝四擁有自己的風格，他可以鼓舞球員。」 <br />\n<br />\n另一主持人Alex Crook認為：「第一，我看不出流著利物浦血液的謝拉特會考慮這份工作。第二，我不知道有多少曼聯球迷會歡迎他來到奧脫福，我一個也看不到。」"},{"pid":"ce2f6c21883b3bfe00c28561a3cb981db7a99668","tid":2268863,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:22:06.000Z","msg":"G持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023331ace8e5c0b036284842de421e46a2a5784c","tid":2268863,"uid":104764,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa14a0cc5c097b153a68253a1d2bb5127a96346","tid":2268863,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"023331ace8e5c0b036284842de421e46a2a5784c","tid":2268863,"uid":104764,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T06:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src